name: hilltop.
description:
tsitsikamma national park, south africa.

i know you can barely see my little brother, but i like it that way.
we had climbed all the way up this huge seaside hill and there was a ledge at the top.

i walked down before him and as i looked back, he was raising his arms high in the air.

o, so high.

each card is 4-3/8" x 5-3/4" and tucked into something earthy: a grocery bag envelope made from 100% recycled materials.

action envelope, the company i buy the envelopes from, is also 100% wind-powered and committed to greener efforts to help keep our earth beautiful.
